These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: folk, punk, indie, trance, r&b, soul, dubstep
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of r&b is between the fan of folk and the fan of indie##2
5. the fan of trance is between the fan of punk and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | indie | r&b | folk | trance | punk | soul |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, reading, puzzles, rock-climbing, cooking, card-games, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is singing##2
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | card-games | magic-tricks | singing | puzzles | rock-climbing | reading | cooking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
