3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is gardening##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | drawing | magic-tricks | cooking | gardening | board-games | video-games | collecting |

